      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782184447055,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "B. ToolRegistry 是统一工具清单\n\n模型只看到“可调用工具”\n不需要知道工具来自哪里\nlist_tools 可以按来源分组说明",
      "fontSize": 19,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "B. ToolRegistry 是统一工具清单\n\n模型只看到“可调用工具”\n不需要知道工具来自哪里\nlist_tools 可以按来源分组说明",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 89,
      "autoResize": false,
      "index": "bBD"
    },
