      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "创建会话时扫描 workspace/skills/*/SKILL.md\n只读取 YAML 元数据：name / description / path\n\n不会默认读取技能正文\n需要时，Agent 用 read 打开对应 SKILL.md",
      "fontSize": 19,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
